overview.en: NZ is a We-Media platform for digital assets,wallets and exchanges.Merchants and players are connected by digital technology to the global knowledge system to provide and share their own facts,results and news ways.
overview.zh: NZ（New Zone-牛币）定位为数字资产的自媒体平台,钱包,交易所,商家和玩家普通大众经由数字科技强化与全球知识体系相连之后,提供与分享他们自身的事实,成果,新闻的途径。
